    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hammers or sticks, plain or with heads, used to sound struck instruments such as drums, dulcimers, and percussion idiophones.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
